      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Ask why the patient is rescheduling. This is optional but helps \nthe clinic with scheduling patterns.\n\nSay something like: \"No problem at all. Is there a particular \nreason for the change, or just a scheduling conflict?\"\n\nAccept ANY answer as valid — this is not a required field:\n- \"Something came up\" → \"Totally understand.\"\n- \"I have a work thing\" → \"No worries at all.\"\n- \"I'd rather not say\" → \"That's completely fine.\"\n- \"I just need a different time\" → \"Got it.\"\n\nDo NOT push for more detail. One ask is enough. \nWhatever they say, acknowledge briefly and move on.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Confirm Collected information",
      "edges": [
        {
          "destination_node_id": "node-1772568867988",
          "id": "edge-1772568821577-0-ucj7f4mpy",
          "transition_condition": {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "Received the user's insurance name"
          }
        }
      ],
      "id": "node-1772568821577",
      "type": "conversation",
      "display_position": {
        "x": 1745.6664297536095,
        "y": 291.46229957738245
      },
      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Read back DOB, phone, reason, preferences.\nExample: \"Let me confirm: I have your date of birth as [DOB], callback at [phone], to be seen for [reason], preferring [days/times] with [provider]. Is that correct?\"\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Final confirmation",
      "edges": [
        {
          "destination_node_id": "component-end-1772567428423",
          "id": "edge-1772568867988-0-lmu1owivx",
          "transition_condition": {
            "type": "prompt",
            "prompt": "Received the user's insurance name"
          }
        }
      ],
      "id": "node-1772568867988",
      "type": "conversation",
      "display_position": {
        "x": 2300.324463723821,
        "y": 304.83168256978206
      },
      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Tell the user that we will get back to them in due course and politely ask if they needed help with anything else.\nExample: \"Perfect. We’ll take a look at the doctor’s schedule and give you a call back soon to let you know when they can see you. Did you need me to help you with anything else?\"\n"
      }
    },
